<p><strong>Sydney, {{ date | readableDate }}</strong>
<p>Oracle and OneQode today announce their partnership to bring joint cloud & network solutions to game industry and enterprise customers in the Asia-Pacific region.</p>
<div class="callout col-xs-12 p-2 my-2" id="key-facts">
	<h2>Key facts</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>The two companies will develop integrated solutions for customers in the Asia-Pacific region</li>
		<li>Oracle will integrate OneQode’s network and cloud services into their Oracle Cloud Infrastructure (OCI) solutions offering</li>
		<li>OneQode will integrate Oracle’s services, including OCI’s database and security products, into their cloud platform</li>
	</ul>
</div>
<p>The companies will jointly develop whole-of-region solutions for game industry and enterprise customers, integrate their service offerings and explore wider opportunities to deliver high-performance solutions for customers in the region.</p>
