<p style="color: #ff9c9d;">“This is the space for a quote (or three) from an Oracle representative about their thoughts on a partnership with OneQode, what it means for customers and the future. OCI is built to deliver better performance for enterprise customers, and we’re pleased to be working with OneQode to deliver high-performance solutions to our customers in the game industry and enterprise space”, says Jane Doe, XYZ at Oracle.</p>
<p>“I’m incredibly excited. Oracle has a global footprint and a significant pedigree. They’ve got a proven track record as an excellent partner,” said Matt Shearing, OneQode CEO. “We see it as a 1 + 1 = 3 moment that allows us to give offerings to customers that they won’t be able to get anywhere else. Ultimately our customers will be the real winners.”</p>
<p>Oracle and OneQode will work to bring combined solutions to their customers, integrate their services and introduce Direct Connect functionality between OCI and OneQode Cloud. Oracle and OneQode will continue to explore new opportunities to bring high-performance connected experiences to customers in the gaming space and beyond.</p>
